to decide, is it ?

346
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:53,800
How long have you been
doing that ?

347
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,000
How many years ?

348
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:57,280
Coming to the apartment.

349
00:24:57,360 --> 00:25:00,200
What about your own life ?

350
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:02,800
What about Sally ?

351
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:06,040
Just wait till I die.

352
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,440
Then you'll have to think
of yourself.

353
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:10,640
How are you going to like that ?

354
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:20,160
Richard...

355
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:25,360
