356
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:27,800
if you felt
well enough to come.

357
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,000
Just to let you know,

358
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:32,040
I am making the crab thing.

359
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:34,960
Not that I imagine
it makes any difference to you.

360
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:36,600
Of course,
it makes a difference.

361
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:37,840
I love the crab thing.

362
00:25:39,560 --> 00:25:41,760
Clarissa ?

363
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:43,880
Yes ?

364
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:59,960
I'll be back at 3:30,

365
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,440
and I'll help you
get dressed.

366
00:26:01,520 --> 00:26:03,640
Wonderful.

367
00:26:03,680 --> 00:26:05,680
3:30.

368
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:18,240
Wonderful.

369
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:45,520
<i>It's on this day,</i>

370
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,680
<i>this day of all days...</i>

371
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:58,520
<i>her fate becomes clear
to her.</i>

372
00:27:05,080 --> 00:27:06,400
