376
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:15,520
I'll be down very soon.

377
00:27:20,120 --> 00:27:22,360
Hmm.

378
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:25,680
What happens is,
she says she wants something,

379
00:27:25,760 --> 00:27:27,160
