I wish I'd been there.

386
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:36,600
I wish you had, too.

387
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,760
Did you give her that look ?

388
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:39,840
That sort of look you do ?

389
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:44,040
