402
00:28:21,360 --> 00:28:22,480
Yes, ma'am.

403
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:24,440
I hadn't forgotten.

404
00:28:26,800 --> 00:28:27,960
China tea, I think.

405
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:32,720
And ginger.

406
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,760
Ginger, Madam ?

407
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,400
I'd like
to give the children a treat.

408
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,560
We'd have to go to London

409
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:47,520
