410
00:28:47,600 --> 00:28:48,840
I haven't finished this,

411
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,760
and there's the rest
of lunch

412
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,200
to get ready.

413
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:55,040
The 12:30 train, Nelly,
will get you

414
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:56,600
into London just after 1:00.

415
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,080
If you return on the 2:30,

416
00:28:58,120 --> 00:29:00,640
