418
00:29:04,560 --> 00:29:05,640
No.

419
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:08,080
Well, then, is something
detaining you, Nelly ?

420
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,840
I can't think of anything
more exhilarating

421
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:20,000
