in the first proof.

426
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:36,000
Lucky to have found them then.

427
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:38,640
<i>Passiondale was a...</i>

428
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:39,800
<i>charnel house</i>

429
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:42,400
<i>from which no min returned.</i>

