00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,840
Do you think it's possible that

431
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,520
bad writing actually
attracts a higher

432
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,400
incidence of error ?

433
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:53,120
If it's all right, I thought
I might take a short walk.

434
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:55,960
Not far ?

435
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,440
No. Just for air.

436
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,240
Go then.

437
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:04,320
If I could walk midmorning,

438
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:05,720
I'd be a happy man.

439
00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:17,440
She'll die.

440
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:20,800
She's going to die.

441
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:25,720
That's what's going to happen.

442
00:30:25,880 --> 00:30:27,240
Huh.

443
00:30:27,320 --> 00:30:28,840
That's it.

444
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:36,440
She'll kill herself.

445
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:41,400
She'll kill herself
over something

446
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:43,240
which doesn't seem to matter.

447
00:30:43,320 --> 00:30:45,760
Let's think.

448
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:47,520
You grease the pan, Mommy.

449
00:30:47,600 --> 00:30:49,600
I know you grease the pan,
sweet one.

450
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,920
Even Mommy knows that.

451
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:55,520
This is what we're going to do.

452
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:57,680
Flour...

453
00:30:57,760 --> 00:31:00,040
bowl...

454
00:31:00,120 --> 00:31:01,200
sifter.

455
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,280
Can I do it, Mommy ?

456
00:31:03,320 --> 00:31:04,840
