457
00:31:06,320 --> 00:31:07,920
Yes, you can sift the flour,
baby,

458
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:09,640
if that's what makes you happy.

459
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,600
Yeah.

460
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:22,400
Isn't it beautiful ?

461
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:25,640
Don't you think
it looks like snow ?

462
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:26,600
Hmm ?

463
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:27,560
Okay.

464
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,880
Now, the next thing...

465
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:31,520
The next thing I'm going

466
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:34,600
to show you... uh, is...

467
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,760
we measure out the cups.

468
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:38,200
Mommy, it isn't that difficult.

469
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,960
Now, I know.
I know it isn't difficult.

470
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:40,960
It's just that I...

471
00:31:41,040 --> 00:31:43,320
I just want to do this
for Daddy.

472
00:31:43,360 --> 00:31:45,240
Because it's his birthday ?

473
00:31:45,280 --> 00:31:46,200
That's right.

474
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,680
We're baking the cake

475
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,600
to show him
that we love him.

476
00:31:49,680 --> 00:31:52,120
Otherwise he won't know
we love him ?

477
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:57,320
That's right.

478
00:32:06,040 --> 00:32:07,680
I got all the stuff.

479
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:09,920
I'm going right out again.

480
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,600
My God, what a zoo !

481
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:14,280
Why do people have to talk
about dry cleaning ?

482
00:32:14,360 --> 00:32:16,400
I mean, what is there
to talk about ?

483
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:18,040
I bought you some flowers.

484
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,440
Where are you ?

485
00:32:21,520 --> 00:32:23,160
In here.

486
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,520
I got someone at work
to cover me.

487
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:28,680
I'll be with you all night.

488
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,040
Are you all right ?

489
00:32:36,120 --> 00:32:37,920
Sure.

490
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:43,400
I guess you saw Richard.

491
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,720
That's right.

492
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:49,040
Well, of course.

493
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:50,960
I bet he said,

