495
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,720
<i>Can I skip the party ?</i>

496
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:56,920
Don't worry.

497
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:58,560
He always shows up.

498
00:32:58,640 --> 00:32:59,640
Oh, sure.

499
00:32:59,720 --> 00:33:00,760
In the end.

500
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:02,520
What, Richard miss an award ?

501
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:04,640
A chance to talk about his work.

502
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:06,040
I don't think so.

503
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,160
He'll show up.

504
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,880
You did the seating.

505
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,680
I did.

506
00:33:13,800 --> 00:33:15,480
I don't believe it...
Louis Waters.

507
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:17,720
Is Louis coming ?

508
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:18,840
Richard's Louis ?

509
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,200
He is.

510
00:33:20,280 --> 00:33:22,200
