511
00:33:24,680 --> 00:33:26,600
Why do I always have
to sit next to the exes ?

512
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:28,440
Is this some kind of a hint,
sweetheart ?

513
00:33:28,520 --> 00:33:30,840
And, anyway, shouldn't
the exes have a table

514
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:34,200
