516
00:33:38,240 --> 00:33:39,600
I'm off.

517
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,520
Try not to pass out
from excitement.

518
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,240
Clarissa...

519
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,520
it's going to be beautiful.

520
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,600
Thank you.

521
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:01,440
You're welcome.

522
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:10,960
