someone at the door !

529
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,760
Hello ?

530
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:53,600
Hello ? Laura ?

531
00:34:53,680 --> 00:34:54,640
Hi, Kitty.

532
00:34:54,720 --> 00:34:55,800
Hi. Am I interrupting ?

533
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,400
Oh, of course not. Come in.

534
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:58,520
Are you all right ?

535
00:34:58,600 --> 00:35:00,080
Why, sure.

536
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:02,200
Hi, Richie.

537
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,320
Sit down.

538
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,760
